AN MLUNGU hunter appeared briefly before the Modimolle Magistrates Court in Limpopo yesterday after he allegedly shot and killed a farm worker while hunting warthogs on Saturday.Limpopo police spokesman Brigadier Motlafela Mojapelo said the man alleged he and his female companion heard movements and fired shots in the same direction. &ldquo;It is alleged that when they reached the spot they found they had shot a human being, who had died on the spot,&rdquo; said Mojapelo. The case was postponed to Thursday for a bail application.